<TD ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP WIDTH="70%">
<H3 ALIGN=CENTER><B><FONT COLOR="#8F982C"><FONT SIZE=+2>&quot;Advantages
of Engaging Ashland Accounting&quot;</FONT></FONT></B></H3>

<CENTER><P>
<HR SIZE=1 WIDTH="100%"></P></CENTER>

<P><FONT COLOR="#8F982C">What sets us apart from &quot;the Big Six&quot;and
other accounting firms?</FONT><FONT COLOR="#FFFFFF"> </FONT></P>

<P><FONT COLOR="#FFFFFF">We are focused, fast and know how to expedite
the compliance issues facing our clients.We have worked with more than
350 different composites in almost every investment style. We work with
each client to create a performance reporting format that is efficient
and accurate. The result: faster production of quarterly performance reporting.
</FONT></P>

<P><FONT COLOR="#FFFFFF">We perform quarterly verifications. Our clients
need to be able to compete in searches requiring independent verification
through the most recent quarter. Quarterly verifications enable the back
office to respond quickly to RFP's, consultant questionnaires and client
review meetings. It ensures compliance reporting is up-to-date and reduces
the risk and embarrassment of having to restate numbers. </FONT></P>

<P><FONT COLOR="#FFFFFF">Ashland Accounting provides services for money
managers and plan sponsors. By remaining abreast of the demands of both
communities, we can respond quickly to new developments affecting our clients.
</FONT></P>

<P><FONT COLOR="#FFFFFF">We make ourselves available every day to answer
questions on AIMR and/or performance-related issues. We invest as much
time in consulting with our clients as we do in verifying their numbers.
</FONT></P>

<P><FONT COLOR="#FFFFFF">Our fees are inclusive. Clients are not billed
by the hour, nor are there additional charges for phone calls or meetings.</FONT></P>

