<H3 ALIGN=CENTER><B><FONT COLOR="#8F982C"><FONT SIZE=+2>&quot;SAS70&quot;<BR>
</FONT><FONT SIZE=+0>The audit that checks to see if the manager is doing
what they tell you they are doing.</FONT></FONT></B><BR>
<BR>

<HR SIZE=1 WIDTH="100%"></H3>

<CENTER><P><FONT COLOR="#8F982C"><FONT SIZE=+1>Other:</FONT></FONT></P></CENTER>

<P><FONT COLOR="#FFFFFF">Consultations and status meetings</FONT></P>

<P><FONT COLOR="#FFFFFF">Drafting of procedures performed and results</FONT></P>

<P><FONT COLOR="#FFFFFF">Review of report</FONT></P>

<P><FONT COLOR="#FFFFFF">Planning/Supervision</FONT></P>

<P><FONT COLOR="#FFFFFF">Recovery and backup procedures<FONT SIZE=+1> </FONT></FONT></P>

<CENTER><P>
<HR SIZE=1 WIDTH="100%"></P></CENTER>

