<H2 ALIGN=CENTER><B><I><FONT COLOR="#408080">Independant Accountant's Verification
Report</FONT></I></B> 
<HR SIZE=1 WIDTH="100%"></H2>

<P><BR>
Board of Directors<BR>
Money Management, Inc.<BR>
Street Address, Suite Number<BR>
City, State Zip <BR>
<BR>
We have examined the performance presentation of the Equity Composite of
Money Management, Inc. from start date through March 31, 1996. We conducted
our examination in accordance with standards established by the American
Institute of Certified Public Accountants and the Association for Investment
Management and Research. <BR>
<BR>
Our examination verified that the composite included all appropriate accounts
and time periods. Our examination also verified the calculation of performance
results. We believe our examination provides a reasonable basis for our
opinion. <BR>
<BR>
In our opinion, the performance presentation of the Equity Composite presents
results that conform, in all material respects, to the Performance Presentation
Standards as adopted by the Association for Investment Management and Research,
Level 1. <BR>
<BR>
Additional information and other mandates required by the Performance Presentation
Standards are an integral part of this opinion. <BR>
<BR>
SAMPLE <BR>
<BR>
Ashland Accounting Services, P.C.<BR>
September 30, 1996</P>

<CENTER><P><BR>
Independent Verification and Attestation for AIMR Performance Presentation
Standards 
<HR SIZE=1 WIDTH="100%"></P></CENTER>

