<P>
<HR SIZE=1 WIDTH="100%"></P>

<UL>
<P><FONT SIZE=-1>Fees are determined by Ashland Accounting Services on
a client by client basis. On average, Level 1 Verifications are $2,500/composite,
Level 2 Verifications are $4,500/composite and Retroactive Verifications
are normally 150% of one year' fees, regardless of how many prior years
are verified.<BR>
<BR>
The level of service individual investment managers require, as well as
how knowledgable the firm is of compliance issues, will affect fees.</FONT></P>

<P><FONT SIZE=-1>One-half of the Retroactive fee must be paid prior to
commencement of services, and the remainder is due upon issuance of our
independent accountant's verification report. On going annual fees will
be due in quarterly installments at the beginning of each quarter.</FONT></P>
</UL>

