<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Where is Misery Bay?</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000080" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#800040">

<TABLE BORDER="0" ALIGN="DEFAULT" WIDTH="100%">
<TR>
<TD><IMG SRC="MBPdk.gif" BORDER="0">
<P ALIGN="left"><IMG SRC="CDI21F1.gif" BORDER="0" WIDTH="350" HEIGHT="10"></P>
</TD>
<TD></TD>
</TR>
<TR>
<TD>Meet the staff of Misery Bay Publications</TD>
<TD></TD>
</TR>
<TR>
<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP" WIDTH="70%">
<P>&nbsp;</P>
<P><B><FONT SIZE="5">W</FONT></B>elcome to our home. We invite you in to sit back and enjoy the view. There is no work to be done, the kids are quietly playing by the channel, and in the distance you watch the freighters gracefully float up and downstream. </P>

<P>When you let the quiet take over, eventually you will want to explore the 10 acres. Take your pick. Walk in the Cedar forest, rocky marshy shore, or down the winding tree lined lanes. Here you will see endangered wild flowers, wild animals, and befuddled fishermen.</P>
<P>During the coming months we will be featuring the wild flowers and stories of our adventures on the bay. When the ice thaws and we can  pick them up, we will have offer our visitors FREE Actual Fossils from the property. So keep you eyes peeled! <I>(If we get a rush, we may make it a contest.)</I></P>
<P><IMG SRC="CDI21F1.gif" BORDER="0" WIDTH="350" HEIGHT="10"></P>
<P><IMG SRC="heron2.gif" HSPACE="1" ALIGN="LEFT">

</P>

<CENTER><P>
<B>News from Misery Bay</B></P></CENTER>


<P>For a while there the brave little blue monkey flowers were shaking off the morning frost, some of them still blooming in the sunshine.  Now they -- and all of the wild flower blossoms -- are resting under  a soft blanket of snow.  While the blooms wait for spring, the ice fishermen are just waiting for the ice to be strong enough.  Then they will be hauling their shanties out on the bay.
There is, however, a new energy in the air.  MBIndustries has some new clients, and we look forward to adding a whole new range of options for our clients.  Watch the opening page for the latest information about this exciting new opportunity.</P>

</TD>
<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP" WIDTH="25%">

<P>&nbsp;
</P>
<CENTER><P><B><FONT COLOR="Black">Where is Misery Bay?</FONT></B></P></CENTER>



<P><FONT COLOR="Black">The heart of Misery Bay Publications is located just east
of Alpena, Michigan on a rocky piece of Lake Huron shoreline known
locally as Misery Bay. Legend has it that one winter in the last
century a ship foundered, and its crew barely survived. With the
spring thaw came the realization that the poor wretches had suffered
great privations only five miles from the bustling settlement
of Alpena.</FONT><IMG SRC="map.gif" HSPACE="1" ALIGN="RIGHT"></P>


<P ALIGN="right">&nbsp;</P>
</TD>
</TR>
<TR>
<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP"></TD>
<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP"></TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>
