<H4><CENTER> So you say that you, your business, or organization
needs a homepage, or maybe a catalog?</CENTER> <CENTER>Misery
Bay is the place, and Jean and Eunice are the answer. </CENTER><CENTER>They
have put together their unique skills to come up with a complete
one-of-a-kind package to help you in cyber space.</CENTER><BR>
</H4>

<H3><EM>Meet the fabulous staff of</EM></H3>

<P>
<CENTER> 
