<H3><CENTER><B>Jean Martin -</B><STRONG> Eunice Link</STRONG>
</CENTER></H3>

<H3><CENTER>Partners <STRONG><I>- the buck stops here!</I></STRONG>
</CENTER></H3>

<H4><CENTER>Jean is a professional writer with experience in newspaper
staff writing, photography, layout, and community relations work.
She has written , edited, and published several books of local
history. She lives north of Lansing in St. Johns, Michigan.</H4>

<H4>Eunice, a computer graphics and fine arts specialist, studied
at Lansing Community College. She has shown and sold art pieces
in galleries at St. Ignace and on Mackinac Island. She lives south
and west of Flint near the village of Gaines.</H4>
