<CENTER><H1>HOW TO PAY FOR MISERY BAY'S SERVICE</H1></CENTER>
<CENTER><H2><STRONG><EM>You may e-mail us.  You may phone us.  You may fax us.</EM></STRONG></H2></CENTER><BR><H3><CENTER>We will answer any and all quesitons. </CENTER>
We can provide you with the Web Site with great graphics, links and forward your e-mail at low rates.  You will need to pay for your first month to start. Then we begin to work on your site.   After we have designed, placed your site on the web and you are satisfied , then your month starts at that point.  We will bill you directly at the begining of each month. <EM> For those paying by credit card we will notify you before we bill again.</EM>

<OL>
<LI><BLINK>	<STRONG>We take Visa or MasterCard.  </STRONG></BLINK><P>
DO NOT SEND YOUR CREDIT CARD NUMBERS BY E-MAIL!  You may fax or phone them to (517)271-8378.  
<LI>
<STRONG>You may pay by check.</STRONG>  Your site will not be started until the check clears.  
</OL></H3>


<EM><STRONG>*After you are up and running, if you pay for the whole year in advance we will give you 2 months free.  12 months for the price of 10!</STRONG></EM>
<HR ALIGN=center SIZE=2>
<H2><CENTER>Need more information?<A HREF="mailto: mail@miserybay.com">     Contact us now!</A></H2><BR><H4>
Misery Bay Publications<BR>
PO Box 539<BR>
Gaines, Michigan 48436-0539<BR>
<EM>phone/fax</EM> (517) 271-8378<BR>
<EM>e-mail: mail@miserybay.com</EM></CENTER>
<STRONG><H5><P>*REMINDER!  DO NOT SEND YOUR CREDIT CARD NUMBERS BY E-MAIL!  This is for your protection.  Thank you.</H4></STRONG>


