<P ALIGN="center"><IMG BORDER="0" SRC="Pub.gif" ALT="Rose Publishing"></P>
<P ALIGN="center"><FONT SIZE="5"><B>Fine-tuned, custom made mailing lists and marketing tips.</B></FONT></P>
<P ALIGN="center"><IMG SRC="CDI8012.gif" BORDER="0"></P>
<P ALIGN="center">
<B><FONT SIZE="+7">One Stop Shopping</FONT></B></P>
<P ALIGN="center"> <IMG SRC="CDI4383.gif" BORDER="0" HSPACE="10" ALIGN="BASELINE"><B><FONT SIZE="5"><A HREF="distribution.htm">Production</A></FONT></B><IMG SRC="CDI4383.gif" BORDER="0" HSPACE="10" ALIGN="BASELINE"><B><FONT SIZE="5"><A HREF="writing.htm">Writing</A></FONT></B><A HREF="writing.htm"><B></B></A><B><IMG SRC="CDI4383.gif" BORDER="0" HSPACE="10" ALIGN="BASELINE"><FONT SIZE="5"><A HREF="distribution.htm">Distribution</A></FONT></B></P>
<TABLE BORDER="0" ALIGN="DEFAULT" WIDTH="100%">
<TR>
<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP" WIDTH="25%">
<P><IMG SRC="CDI6131.gif" BORDER="0"><BR>
