<P ALIGN="left"><IMG SRC="CDI4383.gif" BORDER="0" HSPACE="10" ALIGN="BASELINE" WIDTH="9" HEIGHT="9"><B><FONT SIZE="4"> </FONT></B><FONT SIZE="4">We will use our Bulk Permit (saving you $$$)</FONT><BR>
<IMG SRC="CDI4383.gif" BORDER="0" HSPACE="10" ALIGN="BASELINE" WIDTH="9" HEIGHT="9"><FONT SIZE="4">We sort and bar code your pieces and take  them to the post office. </FONT><BR>
<IMG SRC="CDI4383.gif" BORDER="0" HSPACE="10" ALIGN="BASELINE" WIDTH="9" HEIGHT="9"><FONT SIZE="4"> You will not have to wade through the pages and pages of government rules and regulations-</FONT> <I>and then at the post office - find out your mailing is rejected because your forgot to dot the &quot;i&quot; or cross the &quot;t&quot;. </I><I></I><BR>
 <IMG SRC="CDI4383.gif" BORDER="0" HSPACE="10" ALIGN="BASELINE" WIDTH="9" HEIGHT="9"><FONT SIZE="4">We are CASS and PAVE certified, fully automated.  </FONT><BR>
<IMG SRC="CDI4383.gif" BORDER="0" HSPACE="10" ALIGN="BASELINE" WIDTH="9" HEIGHT="9"><FONT SIZE="4">We can stuff, tab, collate, seal, and mail. </FONT></P>
</TD>
