<P ALIGN="center"><B><FONT SIZE="4">HOW TO PAY FOR MISERY BAY'S SERVICE:</FONT></B><BR>
<B>You may e-mail us. You may phone us. You may fax us.</B></P>
<P>You will need to pay the first months charge to start. We then begin to work on your site. After we have designed, placed your site on the web , and you are satisfied then your month starts at that point. We will bill directly the begining of each month. For those paying by credit card we will notify you before we bill again.<B> *</B><B></B><I><B>After you are up and running, if you choose to pay for the whole year in advance we will give you 2 months free. 11 months for the price of 9! </B></I></P>
<UL>
<LI><B>We take Visa or MasterCard.</B> DO NOT SEND YOUR CREDIT CARD NUMBERS BY E-MAIL! You may fax or phone them to (517)271-8378. We will need the name on the card, your credit card number, and expiration date.</LI>
<LI><B>You may pay by check.</B> Your site will not be started until the check clears. </LI>
</UL>
<P>*REMINDER! DO NOT SEND YOUR CREDIT CARD NUMBERS BY E-MAIL! This is for your protection. Thank you.</P>
