<CENTER><P><A HREF="http://www.marytown.org/index.htm"><B>St. Bonaventure Conventual Franciscan
Province</B></A></P></CENTER>
</TD>
<TD ALIGN="LEFT" VALIGN="TOP">
<CENTER><P><A HREF="http://www.miserybay.com/gaines/village"><B>Village of Gaines</B></A></P></CENTER>
