<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>Peace Education Center</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="multi2.gif" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#FF00FF" VLINK="#408080" ALINK="#FF00FF">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="peace1a.gif"></CENTER>
<CENTER><STRONG><H3>300 west grand river avenue, lansing, michigan 48906<br>phone: 517/485-5544 </H3></STRONG>
<a href="mailto:mail@miserybay.com">mail@miserybay.com. </A><BLINK>Please write <STRONG>PEC</STRONG> in Subject line</BLINK></CENTER>.<HR ALIGN=center SIZE=3><CENTER><BR><IMG SRC="fish2.gif"></CENTER>
<br><STRONG>The Peace Education Center is a Lansing, Michigan (USA) based foundation that organizes initiatives to promote peace locally, nationally and internationally.  We have many different <a href="taskforc.htm">task forces</a> working on different projects, including a group going to help rebuild the churches that were burned in the South, a television program called <A HREF="btl.htm">Between the Lines</A> and various study groups.<p><EM>If you are interested in working with the Peace Education Center -- we are always in need of <A HREF="volunter.htm">volunteer </A>help and motivated individuals willing to actively work on peace projects -- please contact Amy Cairns at the address above.<p>Click on the icons below to see our other pages.

<!-- BUH4ON LINKS --><center><table cellspacing=5 cellpadding=5 border=0><tr><td align=center>
