<P><CENTER>
<H2>Volunteers Needed at PEC</H2></CENTER>
<P>
<H3> &quot;People say, what is the sense of our small effort.
They cannot see that we must lay one brick at a time, take one
step at a time.&quot; -- Dorothy Day</H3>
<P>
<H3>Your Volunteer Help is needed! With so much activity at the
PEC, there is always lots to be done--especially now! Call to
set up a time to come in (as much or as little as you are comfortable
with); we have a wide variety of projects that will benefit from
your help.</H3>
<P>
<H3> Special Thanks to March Volunteers Paul Kelterbaum, Kim Hauze,
Margaret Brattin, Frieda Brown, Bill Petry and Elise Harveyl</H3>
