<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>PEC Anti-Nuclear Campaign</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="mask2.gif" BGCOLOR="#C0C0C0" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#3141CE" VLINK="#408080">

<a name="top"><!-- HEADER -->
<A HREF="index.htm"><img src="dove.gif" align="right" border=0 alt="The Dove of Peace Will Fly"></A> <FONT color="brown" SIZE="+4"><CENTER>PEC Anti-Nuclear Campaign</CENTER></FONT>
<br><hr size=4>
<br clear>
<!-- END HEADER -->
<H4><p><b>T</b>he Peace Eduction Center is involved with groups across the Unites States and Internationally working for an international moratorium on the use and proliferation of nuclear weapons.  Recently we have achieved an important victory : the International Court of Justice has declared the use or threat of nuclear weapons illegal!   Read the <a 
href="release.htm">ICJ Decision Press Release</a> and other documenation below:
<p>
<br>
<!-- DOCUMENTATION LIST -->
<blockquote>
<ul>
<li><b><A HREF="release.htm">Int'l Court of Justice declares Nukes Illegal</A></b> (July 8, 1996) 
<br>After a global initiative the ICJ has "found that nuclear weapons violate the principles and rules of humanitarian law".
<p>
<li><b><a href="judge.htm">Op-Ed on ICJ Decision</a></b> (July 8, 1996) 
<br>
By Robert Brown, the UK Chair of the World Court Project.
<p>
</ul>
</blockquote>
