<HEAD><TITLE>Peace Education Center - Simplicity Gatherings</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="garden2.gif" BGCOLOR="#C0C0C0" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#3141CE" VLINK="#408080">
<a name="top"><!-- HEADER -->
<A HREF="index.htm"><img src="dove.gif" align="right" border=0 alt="The Dove of Peace Will Fly"></A>
<br><hr size=4>
<br clear>
<!-- END HEADER -->


<P><H2>
A Sample of Simplicity . . .</H2>
<P>
<H4>At our Simplicity Gatherings we have been sharing materials,
tips and ideas to  help us all simplify our lives. Here is a small
sample of these suggestions to inspire you!
<P>

Tips from Our Gathering...
<UL>
<LI>Garden/Compost.
<LI>Decide not to Obsess.
<LI>Make your own soap on a rope.
<LI>Make Do or Do Without.
<LI>Remake clothing.
<LI>Buy second hand.
<LI>Drink more tea/herbals, less soda - Make quantities to keep
in the fridge.
<LI>Line-dry your clothes.
<LI>Look at the Big Picture.
<LI>Take time to prepare for your day.
<LI>Give to others.
<LI>Be Grateful.
<LI>Stash your daily change - watch it add up!
<LI>Enjoy the Present.
</UL>

<P>
