<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>Peace Education Center - Where Tax Money Really Goes</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="money.gif" BGCOLOR="#C0C0C0" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#3141CE" VLINK="#408080">

<a name="top"><!-- HEADER -->
<A HREF="index.htm"><img src="dove.gif" align="right" border=0 alt="The Dove of Peace Will Fly"></A>

<!-- END HEADER -->

<CENTER><H3>RESOURCES</H3></CENTER>
<P>

<LI><STRONG>Additional copies of this flyer are available for .10 each
(1-199), 7 cents each (200 or more), 5 cents each (500 plus) plus
postage.</STRONG><P>
<LI><STRONG><EM>Your Telephone Taxes pay for War</EM>, explanatory brochures. 
Single copies free.  Cards to enclose with phone bills, 12 for
$1.00.</STRONG>
<P>
<LI><STRONG>&quot;Our Tax Money, Our Choice: A Call to War Tax Resistence,&quot;
basic brochure on how's and why's of war tax resistance. 10 cents
each.</STRONG>
<P>
<LI><STRONG>&quot;War Tax Resistance: A Guide to Withholding Your Support
from the Military.&quot;  130-page handbook on all aspects of
war tax resistance, available for $12 plus 15% postage.</STRONG>
</UL>
<IMG SRC="angel.gif"ALIGN=left>
<CENTER><H3>War Resisters league<BR>
339 Lafayette St. New York, NY 10012<BR>
(212) 228-0450<BR>
Fax (212) 228-6193<BR>

<H3><EM>email:</EM><STRONG>wrl@igc.apc.org</STRONG></H3> </CENTER>
