<TITLE>Handprint Order Form</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#C0C0C0" LINK="#0000FF" BACKGROUND="Pastel.jpg">
<form method="POST" action="http://www.thenerve2.com/cgi-bin/formmail.pl">
<input type="hidden" name="recipient" value="miseryba@im4u.net">
<input type="hidden" name="subject" value="Handprint Order">
<CENTER><H1> Briggs Library Children's Handprint Online Order Form </H1></CENTER>
<H4>
Order handprint tiles for all of  the children on your Christmas gift list.  
<BR>
Each tile will be displayed in the Children's area when the future Briggs Library opens.
</H4>
<H4>
Donations are <FONT COLOR="Red">$50 each</FONT> for the first two children and<FONT COLOR="Red"> $25</FONT> for each subsequent child in the same family.
<HR>

</H4>


<PRE><H4>
Enter your first name:<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="fname" SIZE="46">
 Enter your last name:<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="lname" SIZE="46">
   Your email address:<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="email" SIZE="46">
       Street Address:<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="street" SIZE="46">
                 City:<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="city" SIZE="12"> State:<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="state" SIZE="14"> ZIP:<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="zip" SIZE="6">

	   Home Phone:<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="hphone" SIZE="13">
           Work Phone:<INPUT TYPE="text" NAME="wphone" SIZE="13">

<HR>

</PRE>
<H4>Please tell us how many handprints you would like to purchase. 
Please recall that in order to qualify for the reduced rate, 
children must be siblings.  </H4>


Number of handprints: 
<SELECT NAME="option">
<OPTION> One child - $50
<OPTION> Two children - $100
<OPTION>  Two children and 1 sibling - $125
<OPTION>  Two children and 2 siblings - $150
<OPTION>  Two children and 3 siblings - $200
<OPTION>  Two children and 4 siblings - $250
<OPTION>  Two children and more than 4 siblings - $300
</OPTION>
</OPTION>
</OPTION>
</OPTION>
</OPTION>
</OPTION>
</OPTION>
</SELECT>
<CENTER><H4>
<I>(We will contact you when the tiles are ready to be made.)</I></H4></CENTER>
<P><HR><P>
<H3>Payment:</H3>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="call" VALUE="phone">By Phone<STRONG>
<BR>I will phone you at 517-224-6168 with my Credit Card number.<P></STRONG>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="check" VALUE="check">By Check<STRONG> 
<BR>I will mail a check to you at the Bement Library, 201 Spring, St. Johhs, MI 48879.</STRONG><P>
