 <H3 ALIGN="center"><B><I><STRONG><BIG>St. Johns, Michigan</BIG></STRONG></I></B></H3>
 <H2 ALIGN="center">Mission Statement</H2>
<P ALIGN="center">&nbsp;
</P>
<H3 ALIGN="center"><I>We are a group of people who love to read and believe that a local library is vital to the health of the community.  To this end we volunteer our time and energy to help energize the community in support of the library, educate the community regarding the library needs.
</I></H3>
