<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>Clinton County Courthouse Brief History</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="backgnd.gif" BGCOLOR="#C0C0C0" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#800040">
<P>
<BODY>

<H1>The Clinton County Courthouse</H1>
<IMG SRC="town.gif" HSPACE=1.5 ALIGN=right ALT="downtown St. Johns">


<H3> <FONT SIZE=+2>E</FONT>ver since the town was platted in 1855, the Courthouse green has been the psychological center of St. Johns, Michigan.  <P>It was here that early settlers left their cattle to graze, where band concerts and patriotic rallies were held, where billboards with important notices are posted, and where the people of St. Johns still meet to  mourn and to celebrate.<P>
Please take a minute to join us in looking back at the history of this venerable landmark  - first through <A HREF = "chouse1.htm"> a brief history </a> and then by following the building's highlights through an <A HREF="chtime.htm"> early timeline</A></H3>
<P><A HREF="index.htm"><IMG SRC="tanhome.gif"><B>Back to St. Johns</B> </a><P>
<HR><HR>
<a href="http://www.miserybay.com/mbay.htm"><H3>Where is Misery Bay anyway?</H3></a>
</ul>
<P>
<H4><center> <I>Page Design by</i><A HREF = "http://www.miserybay.com"> Misery Bay Publications</a><BR>
