<DOCNO>WT06-B11-149</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA033-000674-B038-247</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.entecheng.com:80/dereg.html 205.245.97.204 19970209171707 text/html 5049
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 09 Feb 1997 17:17:14 GMT
