	<TD VALIGN=top ALIGN=left WIDTH=440>

<H2>Governmental - Military</H2>
Entech has provided design services to several military installations on the east coast.  From new natural gas lines to boiler installations and lighting retrofit and heating upgrades, Entech is familiar with the design requirements of US governmental agencies.

	<BR>
	</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>
		
