<CENTER>please e mail our VP of Marketing, <A HREF="mailto:MLloyd@entecheng.novell.net">Matt Lloyd or</A></CENTER>

<CENTER> Water/Wastewater Business Unit Director <A HREF="mailto:RMcMullen@entecheng.novell.net">Ros McMullen</A></CENTER> 

<CENTER>or give us a call at 610-373-6667</CENTER>
