<HTML>
<head>
<title>Moravian College</title>
<meta http-equiv="authoring_tool" content="HotDog">
<meta http-equiv="distribution" content="global">
<meta http-equiv="resource-type" content="document">
</head>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#ff ff ff" LINK="#FF 00 00 " VLINK="#FF 00 00">
<TABLE WIDTH=591 BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0>
<TR>
	<TD COLSPAN=3 WIDTH=440 HEIGHT=15>
	</TD>
	<TD WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=15>
	<IMG SRC="graphics/150x15.gif" BORDER=0 WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=15>
	</TD>
</TR>	
<TR>
	<TD WIDTH=50>
	</TD> 

	<TD VALIGN=top ALIGN=left WIDTH=100>
	<IMG SRC="graphics/morav4.jpg" BORDER=0 WIDTH=100 HEIGHT=100>
	</TD>

	<TD VALIGN=middle ALIGN=left WIDTH=290>
	<H4><IMG SRC="graphics/5x5.gif" BORDER=0>Moravian College
	<BR><IMG SRC="graphics/5x5.gif" BORDER=0>Campus-wide energy audit
	<BR><IMG SRC="graphics/5x5.gif" BORDER=0>Hall of Science Building
                     <BR><IMG SRC="graphics/5x5.gif" BORDER=0>Chiller System Analysis</H4>
	</TD>

	<TD  VALIGN=top ALIGN=left WIDTH=150>
	<BR><TABLE WIDTH=150 BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0>
		<TR ALIGN=left>			
			<TD WIDTH=10%>
			<A HREF="../index.html">
			<IMG SRC="graphics/diamond.gif" BORDER=0></A>
			</TD>
			<TD WIDTH=90%>
			<A HREF="../index.html">Main Menu</A>
			</TD>
		</TR>
		</TABLE>
	</TD>
</TR>
<TR>
	<TD WIDTH=50>
	</TD> 

	<TD VALIGN=top ALIGN=left WIDTH=100>
	</TD>

	<TD COLSPAN=2 VALIGN=middle ALIGN=left WIDTH=440>
		<HR>
		<B>Campus-wide Energy Audit </B>: Entech conducted an Energy Audit for the entire campus.  The Technical Assistance Study consisted of surveying twelve (12) building comprised of more than 400,000 S.F. of gross building area.  Fifteen Energy Conservation Opportunities (ECOs) were identified with annual energy savings of over $375,000 and an average simple payback of 2.6 years with construction costs totaling approximately $987,000.<P>

	Entech prepared the Energy Conservation Measure (ECM) Grant Application for participation in Cycle XV of the grant program and was successful in assisting Moravian College in obtaining a $70,000 ECM Grant for an Energy Management System (EMS).<P>

	Entech provided engineering and design services for the installation of the Energy Management System.  The EMS system consists of approximately 130 points.  Entech evaluated the instrumentation and controls in each building to determine existing conditions.  A list of control points were developed for each building, with a description of how each control/monitoring point will operate and interface with existing controls.  Construction costs estimated at $160,000.
		<P>
		<P><B>Hall of Science Building</B>:Entech updated the Technical Assistance Report for the Hall of Science Building.  Six (6) Energy Conservation Opportunities were identified with annual energy savings of over $50,000 and an average simple payback of 4.2 years with construction costs totaling approximately $210,000.<P>

	Of the six (6) ECOs identified, Moravian College has elected to seek an ECM Grant for a Variable Air Volume System.  The VAV system will reduce annual energy costs by approximately $41,000 with a simple payback of 4.5 years and construction costs totaling approximately $186,000.  Entech prepared and submitted the ECM Grant Application for Cycle XVI Funding.  Entech was successful in obtaining a $75,000 ECM Grant for the implementation of the VAV system.  Construction costs are estimated to be approximately $250,000.<BR><P>

<STRONG>Chiller System Analysis</STRONG>: Entech conducted an analysis of the existing chilled water system serving the Hall of Science Building.  The analysis included the investigation of the existing system and its effectiveness in both performance and useful service life.  The chiller analysis not only examined the existing system, but also investigated alternative chilled water systems which included reciprocating, centrifugal, screw, absorption, and thermal storage.  Analysis was completed in September 1993.<P>

<CENTER>Contact:  Mr. Douglas Plotts, Director of Physical Plant; (610) 861-1495</CENTER>.



		<P><A HREF="../college.html">Return to the Entech College list</A><p>
                                    <a href="http://www.moravian.edu/">Go to Moravian College Page</a>

	</TD>

</TR>
</TABLE>	
<P>
