<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>What Does the Arbor Day Foundation Do?</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff" LINK="#8e2323" VLINK="#84590c"><CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/weblogo_small.gif" ALT="The National Arbor Day Foundation" WIDTH="469" HEIGHT="40"><IMG SRC="./activities.gif" "What Does the Arbor Day Foundation Do?" WIDTH="469" HEIGHT="89"><P><HR WIDTH=469><P><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=469 CELLPADDING=0><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP>The National Arbor Day Foundation is involved in much more than just Arbor Day celebrations around the world. Its mission is to help promote tree care and conservation and to educate people on tree issues. Click on any of the following topics to learn more about the many ways in which The National Arbor Day Foundation helps to make our world more beautiful and more environmentally sound.<P><HR><P><H2><A HREF="./programs/programs.html">Arbor Day Foundation Programs</A></H2><P>Learn more about six nationally recognized programs that promote responsible tree stewardship in communities, on farms and open space, and in the rain forests.<P><HR><P><H2><A HREF="./awards/awards.html">Arbor Day Awards</A></H2><P>Find out about the winners of the 1996 Arbor Day Awards competition, which recognizes outstanding individuals and organizations for their contributions to tree planting and wise environmental stewardship.<P><HR><P><H2><A HREF="ad_farm/ad_farm.html">Arbor Day Farm</A></H2><P>Take a trip to Nebraska City, the birthplace of Arbor Day for a unique educational experience in a superb historical and natural setting.<P><HR><P><IMG SRC="../images/coming.gif" ALT="Coming Soon!"><P><H2>Partnerships for Trees</H2><P>Ways to combine forces with the Foundation to promote tree planting and provide effective educational programs about trees.<P><HR><P><H2>What's New at the Arbor Day Foundation?</H2><P><IMG SRC="../images/coming.gif" ALT="Coming Soon!"><P>A look at the latest goings-on in the world of trees and tree stewardship.<P><HR><P></TD></TR></TABLE><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=469 CELLPADDING=0><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT><A HREF="../join/free_trees.html"><IMG SRC="../images/free_trees_button.gif" ALT="Get 10 Free Trees!" BORDER="0" WIDTH="193" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD><TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="../index.html"><IMG SRC="../images/homepage_button.gif" ALT="Return to Homepage" BORDER="0" WIDTH="70" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF="../join/rainforest.html"><IMG SRC="../images/rainforest_button.gif" ALT="Help Rescue the Rainforest!" BORDER="0" WIDTH="193" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD></TABLE></CENTER></BODY></HTML>
