<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Arbor Day Farm</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff" LINK="#8e2323" VLINK="#84590c"><CENTER><IMG SRC="../../images/weblogo_small.gif" ATL="The National Arbor Day Foundation" WIDTH="469" HEIGHT="40"><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=469 CELLPADDING=0><TD ALIGN=LEFT><IMG SRC="images/ad_farm_logo.gif" ALT="Arbor Day Farm" WIDTH="253" HEIGHT="108"><BR><HR><P>Arbor Day Farm was once the agricultural estate of Arbor Day founder J. Sterling Morton. Along with many of the original barns, buildings, and orchards, the farm now includes interpretive tree trails, a working apple processing operation, and the beautiful and environmentally friendly Lied Conference Center. Visitors may also visit a state-of-the-art fuelwood plant and a demonstration area showing living examples of how to use trees for best land and soil conservation.<P><A HREF="ad_farm.map"><IMG SRC="images/ad_farm.gif" BORDER="0" ISMAP WIDTH="469" HEIGHT="314"></A><P></TABLE><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=469 CELLPADDING=0><TR><TD COLSPAN=3 ALIGN=LEFT>If your browser does not support image maps, just click on the topics below:<P><CENTER><A HREF="./lied_center.html">Lied Conference Center</A><BR><A HREF="./fuelwood_plant.html">Fuelwood Energy Plant</A><BR><A HREF="./steinhart_lodge.html">Steinhart Lodge</A><BR><A HREF="./conservation_demo.html">Conservation Trees Demonstration Area</A><BR><A HREF="./morton_barns.html">Morton Historic Barns</A><BR><A HREF="./apple_house.html">Apple House</A><BR><A HREF="./arbor_lodge.html">Arbor Lodge State Park</A><BR><A HREF="./tree_trails.html">Interpretive Tree Trails</A></CENTER><P><HR><P></TD></TR><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT><A HREF="../../join/free_trees.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/free_trees_button.gif" ALT="Get 10 Free Trees!" BORDER="0" WIDTH="193" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD><TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="../../index.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/homepage_button.gif" ALT="Return to Homepage" BORDER="0" WIDTH="70" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF="../../join/rainforest.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/rainforest_button.gif" ALT="Help Rescue the Rainforest!" BORDER="0" WIDTH="193" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD></TABLE></CENTER> </BODY></HTML>
