<HTML>

<HEAD><TITLE>Information Packets</TITLE></HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff" LINK="#8e2323" VLINK="#84590c">

<CENTER>

<IMG SRC="../images/weblogo_small.gif" ALT="The National Arbor Day Foundation" WIDTH="469" HEIGHT="40"><BR>

<IMG SRC="./images/information_packets.gif" ALT="Information Packets" WIDTH="469" HEIGHT= "89"><P>

<A NAME="celebrate"><HR WIDTH=469></A><P>

<TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=469 CELLPADDING=0>

<TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP><IMG SRC="./images/celebrate_packet.gif"><P></TD>

<TD ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP><H2>Celebrate Arbor Day!</H2>

This free information packet is a great resource for anyone planning an Arbor Day celebration or event.  It includes suggestions for planning an Arbor Day ceremony, a brief history of Arbor Day, a proclamation for the local mayor, as well as appropriate quotes, poems, and even an Arbor Day play.  The packet is full of ideas and even includes a selected bibliography.<P>

<B>Item # 1190 (FREE!)</B><P>
&#128; <A HREF="./ed_order_print.html">Go to Print-Out Order Form</A><P></TD></TR>

<TR><TD COLSPAN=2 ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP><A NAME="fundraising"><HR></A><P>

<H2>Fundraising Trees Information Package</H2>

A packet outlining a unique fundraising project for groups who want to raise money, beautify the environment, and make young people more aware of the importance of trees.<P>

<B>Item # 1309 (FREE!)</B><P>
&#128; <A HREF="./ed_order_print.html">Go to Print-Out Order Form</A><P>

<A NAME="sampler"><HR></A><P>

<H2>Education Materials Sampler</H2>

This sampler of the Arbor Day Foundation's educational materials includes sample brochures for <A HREF="./booklets_etc.html#america">Trees for America</A>, <A HREF="./booklets_etc.html#conservation">Conservation Trees</A> and <A HREF="./booklets_etc.html#rainforest">Rain Forest Rescue</A>, a sample Tree City USA Bulletin, &quot;Trees for America&quot; sheet music, a &quot;Celebrate Arbor Day!&quot; mini-poster, and other materials.<P>

<B>Item # 1178 (FREE!)</B><P>
&#128; <A HREF="./ed_order_print.html">Go to Print-Out Order Form</A><P></TD></TR>

</TABLE><HR WIDTH=469><P>

