<HTML><TITLE>Fuelwood Plant</TITLE><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="8E2323" VLINK="84590C"><CENTER><IMG SRC="../../images/weblogo_small.gif" ALT="The National Arbor Day Foundation"><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=469 CELLPADDING=0><TD ALIGN=LEFT COLSPAN=2><FONT SIZE=+4><B>Fuelwood Energy Plant</B></FONT><BR><HR><P></TD></TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP>Growing trees for fuelwood is a job-creating technology that uses renewable resources and helps the environment.  The fuelwood energy plant has a visitors gallery where you can see how wood chips, and recycled paper and cardboard, fuel the conference center's boilers and provide heating and cooling for <A HREF="./lied_center.html">Lied Conference Center</A>.</TD></TR></TABLE><IMG SRC="./images/fuelwood_plant.gif"><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=469 CELLPADDING=0><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP><OL><LI>Chipped wood is brought by truck.<LI>Scrapers and augers move chips automatically toward the burner.<LI>A metered conveyer delivers the fuel in the exact amounts needed for current energy demands.<LI>Chips are mixed with air in the combustion chamber for an efficient burn.<LI>Circulating water is heated in the boiler, giving off steam under high pressure that heats the conference center in winter, drives the cooling unit in the summer, and heats water year-round.<LI><A HREF="./thepage.html">Ashes are removed and spread on fields and tree plantations to recycle soil nutrients.</A><LI>Particulates are removed from boiler exhausts, with gases--mostly water vapor--passing up the chimney.<BR></OL></TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN=2><HR><P></TD><TR></TABLE><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=469 CELLPADDING=0><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT><A HREF="../../join/free_trees.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/free_trees_button.gif" ALT="Get 10 Free Trees!" BORDER="0" WIDTH="193" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD><TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="../../index.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/homepage_button.gif" ALT="Return to Homepage" BORDER="0" WIDTH="70" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF="../../join/rainforest.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/rainforest_button.gif" ALT="Help Rescue the Rainforest!" BORDER="0" WIDTH="193" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD></TABLE></CENTER>
</DOC>
