<HTML><TITLE>Apple House and Orchard</TITLE><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="8E2323" VLINK="84590C"><CENTER><IMG SRC="../../images/weblogo_small.gif" ALT="The National Arbor Day Foundation"><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=469 CELLPADDING=0><TD ALIGN=LEFT COLSPAN=3><FONT SIZE=+4><B>Apple House and Orchard</B></FONT><BR><HR><P></TD></TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT><IMG SRC="./images/apple_house.gif"><P></TD><TD><PRE>   </PRE></TD><TD ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP>Visit Arbor Day Farm's Apple House during a fall weekend and you'll find yourself in the midst of a whirlwind of old-fashioned apple harvest activities.  Catch the action as fresh-picked apples are washed, sorted, graded and packed on &quot;Rube,&quot; a home-grown mechanical marvel with sounds, motion, and aromas that bring back another era.  Watch as apples are grated and pressed into cider, and then enjoy a cup of the finished product. There's also a gift shop featuring apple-oriented wares (what else?), and an old-fashioned apple retail stand where you can take home a single apple or a bushel.  A stop at the Apple House is a must for any visit to Arbor Day Farm.</TD></TR><TD COLSPAN=3><HR><P></TD></TR></TABLE><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=469 CELLPADDING=0><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT><A HREF="../../join/free_trees.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/free_trees_button.gif" ALT="Get 10 Free Trees!" BORDER="0" WIDTH="193" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD><TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="../../index.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/homepage_button.gif" ALT="Return to Homepage" BORDER="0" WIDTH="70" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF="../../join/rainforest.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/rainforest_button.gif" ALT="Help Rescue the Rainforest!" BORDER="0" WIDTH="193" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD></TABLE></CENTER>
