<HTML><TITLE>Arbor Lodge State Park</TITLE><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="8E2323" VLINK="84590C"><CENTER><IMG SRC="../../images/weblogo_small.gif" ALT="The National Arbor Day Foundation"><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=469 CELLPADDING=0><TD ALIGN=LEFT COLSPAN=3><FONT SIZE=+4><B>Arbor Lodge State Park</B></FONT><BR><HR><P></TD></TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT><IMG SRC="./images/arbor_lodge.gif"><P></TD><TD><PRE>   </PRE></TD><TD ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP>Arbor Lodge, a Nebraska State Historical Park, was the home and estate of J. Sterling Morton, who originated the Arbor Day idea more than a century ago.  Beginning as a simple frontier home, the house was added upon over the years, eventually becoming the graceful mansion visitors see today. Enjoy a walk into the past with a tour of the Mansion and Carriage House, or wander through the beautifully landscaped grounds, including formal gardens and an arboretum featuring hundreds of magnificent trees, many planted by Mr. Morton himself.</TD></TR><TD COLSPAN=3><HR><P></TD></TR></TABLE><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=469 CELLPADDING=0><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT><A HREF="../../join/free_trees.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/free_trees_button.gif" ALT="Get 10 Free Trees!" BORDER="0" WIDTH="193" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD><TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="../../index.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/homepage_button.gif" ALT="Return to Homepage" BORDER="0" WIDTH="70" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF="../../join/rainforest.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/rainforest_button.gif" ALT="Help Rescue the Rainforest!" BORDER="0" WIDTH="193" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD></TABLE></CENTER>
