<HTML><TITLE>Historic Morton Barns</TITLE><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="8E2323" VLINK="84590C"><CENTER><IMG SRC="../../images/weblogo_small.gif" ALT="The National Arbor Day Foundation"><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=469 CELLPADDING=0><TD ALIGN=LEFT COLSPAN=3><FONT SIZE=+4><B>Historic Morton Barns</B></FONT><BR><HR><P></TD></TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT><IMG SRC="./images/morton_barns.gif"><P></TD><TD><PRE>   </PRE></TD><TD ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP>Originally constructed in the early 1900s, the Historic Morton Barns once housed the draft animals and livestock of the Morton farm and orchards. They have been faithfully restored to their early twentieth century appearance and serve as the Foundation's youth curriculum laboratory and as home to it's popular youth Discovery Camps. The barns are also popular for barbecues, square dances, and other informal events.</TD></TR><TD COLSPAN=3><HR><P></TD></TR></TABLE><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=469 CELLPADDING=0><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT><A HREF="../../join/free_trees.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/free_trees_button.gif" ALT="Get 10 Free Trees!" BORDER="0" WIDTH="193" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD><TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="../../index.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/homepage_button.gif" ALT="Return to Homepage" BORDER="0" WIDTH="70" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF="../../join/rainforest.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/rainforest_button.gif" ALT="Help Rescue the Rainforest!" BORDER="0" WIDTH="193" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD></TABLE></CENTER>
