<HTML><TITLE>Conservation Trees Demonstration Area</TITLE><BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="8E2323" VLINK="84590C"><CENTER><IMG SRC="../../images/weblogo_small.gif" ALT="The National Arbor Day Foundation"><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=469 CELLPADDING=0><TD ALIGN=LEFT COLSPAN=3><FONT SIZE=+4><B>Conservation Trees<BR>Demonstration Area</B></FONT><BR><HR><P></TD></TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT><IMG SRC="../../images/leaf_poplar.gif"><P></TD><TD><PRE>   </PRE></TD><TD ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP>Located on a series of rolling hills separated by wooded ravines, the Conservation Trees Demonstration Area features a number of plantings and operations that demonstrate good practice in the use of trees for energy conservation and erosion control.  Walk through the Windbreak Arboretum to see how an effective farmstead windbreak is laid out, or see the Fuelwood Plantation, where fast-growing trees are planted and harvested in planned cycles to provide fuel for the state-of-the art <A HREF="./fuelwood_plant.html">Fuelwood Energy Plant</A> at Arbor Day Farm's <A HREF="./lied_center.html">Lied Conference Center</A>.</TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN=3><HR><P></TD><TR></TABLE><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=469 CELLPADDING=0><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT><A HREF="../../join/free_trees.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/free_trees_button.gif" ALT="Get 10 Free Trees!" BORDER="0" WIDTH="193" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD><TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="../../index.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/homepage_button.gif" ALT="Return to Homepage" BORDER="0" WIDTH="70" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF="../../join/rainforest.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/rainforest_button.gif" ALT="Help Rescue the Rainforest!" BORDER="0" WIDTH="193" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD></TABLE></CENTER>
</DOC>
