<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Conferences and Training</TITLE></HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff" LINK="#8e2323" VLINK="#84590c"><CENTER><IMG SRC="../../images/weblogo_small.gif" ALT="The National Arbor Day Foundation WIDTH="469" HEIGHT= "40"><BR><IMG SRC="images/conferences_and_training.gif" ALT="Conferences and Training" WIDTH="469" HEIGHT="70"><P><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=469 CELLPADDING=0><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT VALIGN=TOP>One of the Foundation's important goals is to convene conferences at Arbor Day Farm to find creative solutions to the complex problems facing trees and the environment. Conferences at Lied Conference Center have addressed topics such as planting trees, community forestry, sustainable agriculture, trees and utilities, educating youth about trees, forest stewardship, trees and the law, and biomass for energy.<P></TD></TR><P></TABLE><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=469 CELLPADDING=0><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT><A HREF="../../join/free_trees.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/free_trees_button.gif" ALT="Get 10 Free Trees!" BORDER="0" WIDTH="193" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD><TD ALIGN=CENTER><A HREF="../../index.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/homepage_button.gif" ALT="Return to Homepage" BORDER="0" WIDTH="70" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT><A HREF="../../join/rainforest.html"><IMG SRC="../../images/rainforest_button.gif" ALT="Help Rescue the Rainforest!" BORDER="0" WIDTH="193" HEIGHT="40"></A></TD></TABLE></CENTER> </BODY></HTML>
