<P><IMG SRC="l_blue.gif" HEIGHT=20 WIDTH=20>&nbsp;<A HREF="phillips/whatsnew.html">What's
New?</A></P>
</TD>

<TD NOWRAP><IMG SRC="l_blue.gif" HEIGHT=20 WIDTH=20>&nbsp;<A HREF="amiphome.html">AMIP: Atmospheric
Model Intercomparison Project</A>

