   <TITLE> PCMDI Publications </TITLE>
   <META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Mozilla/3.01Gold (Win95; I) [Netscape]">
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="bg9.gif">

<P><B><FONT SIZE=+2>PCMDI Publications<IMG SRC="bookshlf.gif" HEIGHT=75 WIDTH=279></FONT></B>

<HR></P>

<P>PCMDI staff publish their work in an international <A HREF="../phillips/PCMDIreports.html">report
series</A> and in the <A HREF="../phillips/PCMDIpapers.html">reviewed literature</A>,
as well as in the proceedings of national and international conferences.
</P>

