<HTML>
<HEAD>
   <TITLE>PCMDI Software Tools</TITLE>
   <META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Mozilla/3.0Gold (Win95; I) [Netscape]">
</HEAD>
<BODY TEXT="#000000" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" LINK="#0000EE" VLINK="#551A8B" ALINK="#FF0000" BACKGROUND="bg9.gif">

<P><IMG SRC="sft.gif" ALT="PCMDI SOFTWARE" HEIGHT=206 WIDTH=204 ALIGN=ABSCENTER><FONT COLOR="#0000FF"><B><FONT SIZE=+2>&nbsp;&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT></B><FONT SIZE=+3>PCMDI Software Tools
</FONT></FONT></P>

<P>
<HR WIDTH="100%">An important component of PCMDI's work is the development,
testing, and distribution of software tools for the storage, diagnosis,
and visualization of data. These include tools for data I/O management
(historically DRS--now superceded by cdunif, EzGet, and LATS); tools for
data visualization and computation (VCS); and tools for the transfer of
data across different formats and visualization platforms (DDI). See the
<A HREF="phillips/PCMDIsoftware.html">Overview</A> for further general information
on PCMDI's software products.</P>

<P>Click on the icons below to obtain information, version updates, technical
support, and ftp retrieval information for the desired PCMDI software tools.</P>

<CENTER><TABLE BORDER=8 CELLSPACING=2 >
<TR ALIGN=CENTER VALIGN=CENTER>
<TD><A HREF="williams/ddi/ddi.html"><IMG SRC="ddi_3.gif" HEIGHT=55 WIDTH=118 ALIGN=CENTER></A></TD>

<TD><A HREF="drach/DRS.html"><IMG SRC="drs3.jpg" BORDER=0 HEIGHT=61 WIDTH=128></A></TD>

<TD><A HREF="ktaylor/ezget/ezget.html"><IMG SRC="ezgt3.jpg" HEIGHT=51 WIDTH=118 ALIGN=CENTER></A></TD>

<TD><A HREF="amip2/lats/latstemp.html"><IMG SRC="lats3.jpg" HEIGHT=51 WIDTH=118 ALIGN=CENTER></A></TD>

<TD><A HREF="williams/vcs/vcshome.html"><IMG SRC="vcs3.jpg" HEIGHT=51 WIDTH=118 ALIGN=CENTER></A></TD>
</TR>
</TABLE></CENTER>

