<head><title>Climate Modeling Infrastructure</title></head>
<body background="blue_paper.gif">
<h1>Climate Modeling Infrastructure</h1>
<hr>
<p>
PCMDI staff members devote a significant share of their time to the development of climate modeling infrastructure, by which we mean the collection of methods and tools for the diagnosis, validation and intercomparison of global climate models.  Examples include ongoing construction of <A HREF="documentation.html">documentation</A>, <A HREF="validation.html">validation data and analysis tools</A>, and <A HREF="PCMDIsoftware.html">software products</A> designed specifically for global climate modeling and analysis.



<p>
<hr>
<a href=../PCMDItoc.html>Return to PCMDI directory</a>
