Keup, A. A. Lacis, H. Le Treut, X.-Z. Liang, J.-F. Mahfouf, B. J. McAvaney,
V. P. Meleshko, J. F. B. Mitchell, J -J. Morcette, P. M. Norris, D. A.
Randall, L. Rikus, E. Roeckner, J.-F. Royer, U. Schlese, D. A. Sheinin, J. M.
Slingo, A. P. Sokolov, K. E. Taylor, W. M. Washington, R. T. Wetherald and I.
Yagai, 1991:  Interpretation of snow-climate feed-back as produced by 17
general circulation models, <i>Science</i>,  <b>253</b>, 888-892.

<p>

