<BR>

<HR WIDTH="100%"><A NAME="Table of Contents"></A><B>Table of Contents<BR>
<BR>
</B><A HREF="#Abstract">Abstract<BR>
</A><A HREF="#1.  INTRODUCTION">1.&nbsp;INTRODUCTION<BR>
</A><A HREF="#2.   THE MODELS AND">2.&nbsp;THE&nbsp;MODELS&nbsp;AND&nbsp;DATA<BR>
</A><A HREF="#3.  CLIMATOLOGICAL">3.&nbsp;CLIMATOLOGICAL STRUCTURES<BR>
</A><A HREF="#4.  INTRASEASONAL OSCILLATION CASE">4.&nbsp;INTRASEASONAL
