</A><A HREF="#5.  MAINTENANCE OF THE INTRASEASONAL OSCILLATION">5.&nbsp;MAINTENANCE
OF THE INTRASEASONAL OSCILLATION<BR>
</A><A HREF="#6.  THE INTRASEASONAL OSCILLATION: A COUPLED">6.&nbsp;THE
INTRASEASONAL OSCILLATION:&nbsp;&nbsp;A COUPLED MODE?<BR>
