Amer. Meteor. Soc.</I>, <B>77</B>: 437-471.</P>

<P><B>Mock, D. R.,</B> S. Hankin, C. B. Baker, J. Davison, and K. Searight,
1996: The Cooperative Ocean-Atmosphere Research Data Service (COARDS):
A virtual data center on the World Wide Web. Preprints, 12 IIPS Conference,
American Meteorological Society, Boston, MA, 393-396. <A HREF="http://ferret.wrc.noaa.gov/noaa_coop/coop_cdf_profile.html">http://ferret.wrc.noaa.gov/noaa_coop/coop_cdf_profile.html</A></P>

<P><B>Phillips, T. J., </B>1994: A summary documentation of the AMIP Models.
PCMDI Report No. 18, LLNL, UCRL-ID-116384, CA, 343 pp. For the most up-to-date
version see WWW address: <A HREF="http://www-pcmdi.llnl.gov/phillips/modldoc/amip/amip.html">http://www-pcmdi.llnl.gov/phillips/modldoc/amip/amip.html.</A></P>

