<html><head><title>AMIP Model History Data</title></head>
<body background="blue_paper.gif">
<h1>AMIP Model History Data</h1>
<hr>
<p>
AMIP model history data (usually at 6-hourly intervals) are provided by PCMDI to those <a href=../phillips/AMIPsubprojects.html>AMIP subprojects</a> that require frequent time samples for their analysis.
<p>
The current processing/distribution status of AMIP model history data is as follows:
<p>
<pre>
<b>
Model		Status
</b>
CSU		Distributed to the subprojects
<p>
ECMWF	        Distributed to the subprojects
<p>
CSIRO	        Distributed to the subprojects	
<p>
MRI	        Distributed to the subprojects	
<p>
UGAMP		Distributed to the subprojects 
<p>
UKMO		Distributed to the subprojects 
<p>
DERF	        Distributed to the subprojects 
<p>
GLA	        Distributed to the subprojects 
<p>
GFDL	        Distributed to the subprojects
<p>
BMRC	        Distributed to the subprojects 
<p>
CCC	        Distributed to the subprojects 
<p>
GSFC	        Distributed to the subprojects 
<p>
COLA	        Distributed to the subprojects 
<p>
</pre>
<p>
