<h1> Access to Referenced Documents</h1>
<hr>
<p>
<p>
Several of the documents referenced in the <A HREF="amipnl8.html">AMIP II guidelines</A> are
not readily available. Some examples are:
<P>
Hess, G. D., R. A. Colman and B. J. McAvaney, 1995: On computing screen temperatures,
humidities and anemometer-height winds in large-scale models. <I>Aust. Met. Mag.</I>, <b>44</B>, 139-145.
<P>
