Vertical interpolation and truncation of
model-coordinate data. NCAR Technical Note NCAR/TN-396+STR, 54 pp.
<P><BR>
AMIP participants may request references such as these from the AMIP Project Office (<a href="mailto:amip@pcmdi.llnl.gov">amip@pcmdi.llnl.gov</a>).     
When making a request, please identify the article(s) to be forwarded, and provide a complete mailing address.

