<P><A NAME="Top of Page"></A></P>

<H1>Documentation Template for AMIP II Experimental Implementation, Model
Output, and Model Characteristics</H1>

<P>
<HR></P>

<H3><A NAME="Disclaimer"></A><B>Disclaimer</B></H3>

<P><I><B>Note: This is a working document that is intended to stimulate
discussion about the necessary content and level of detail for documenting
the features of the participating AMIP II models and their output, as well
as other aspects of experimental implementation. Revisions are anticipated,
based on comments of AMIP&nbsp;II&nbsp;participants. Please send comments
to Tom Phillips </B>(<A HREF="mailto:phillips@pcmdi.llnl.gov">phillips@pcmdi.llnl.gov</A>).</I></P>

<P><B><I>Last update February 13, 1997.</I></B></P>

<P>
<HR WIDTH="100%"></P>

<P><I>AMIP II Modeling Group Representatives are requested to supply the
following contact information and documentation of experimental implementation,
model output, and model characteristics used for the AMIP II Experiment.
Please provide bibliographic information on references whereever relevant.</I></P>

<P><I>See also <A HREF="#Further Instructions">further instructions</A>
after this document becomes final.</I></P>

<P>
<HR WIDTH="100%"></P>

