<head><title>AMIP Scientific Conference/Proceedings</title></head>
<body background="blue_paper.gif">
<h1>AMIP Scientific Conference/Proceedings</h1>
<hr>
<br>
The first AMIP Scientific Conference was held 15-19 May 1995 in Monterey, California.  The Conference provided a forum for the comprehensive examination of AMIP modeling results to date.   
A collection of presentation abstracts is available <a href=../phillips/PCMDIcommunicns.html>on request</a> from PCMDI.
<P>
<A NAME="AMIP_Proceedings"></A>
The Proceedings of the AMIP Scientific Conference have been published as a report of the World Climate Research Programme (<A HREF="http://www.wmo.ch/web/wcrp/wcrp-home.html">WCRP</A>): 
<P>
<I>Proceedings of the First International AMIP Scientific Conference</I>
<BR>
(Monterey, California, USA, 15-19 May 1995)
<BR>
WCRP-92, WMO/TD-No. 732, 532 pp.
<P>
<I>To request a copy of these Proceedings, contact:</I>
<P>
Joint Planning Staff for WCRP
<BR>
41 Avenue Giuseppe Motta
<BR>
Case Postale No. 2300
<BR>
CH-1211 Geneva 20
<BR>
Switzerland
<BR>
Phone: +41-22-730-8418
<BR>
Fax: +41-22-730-734-0357
<BR>
E-mail: <A HREF="mailto:jps@wcrp2.wmo.ch">jps@wcrp2.wmo.ch</A>

<p>
<hr>
