<TITLE>AMIP Abstracts Archive</TITLE> </HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="blue_paper.gif">
<H1>AMIP Abstracts Archive</H1>
<HR>
<P><BR>
<B>For browsers supporting Frames:</B>
<P>
<A HREF="mccravy/AMIPFolder/Abfolder/dean3a.htm">Abstracts Indexed by Author/Subject</A> 
<P><BR>
<B>For browsers not supporting Frames:</b>
<P>
<A HREF="mccravy/AMIPFolder/Abfolder/v_left.html">Abstracts Indexed by Author</A>
<BR>
<A HREF="mccravy/AMIPFolder/Abfolder/absub.htm">Abstracts Indexed by Subject</A>

<P><BR>
<H4>A Note to Authors of AMIP-Related Publications:</H4>

In order to comprehensively summarize analyses of AMIP model simulations to date, authors of AMIP-related publications that are <I>not</I> included herein are strongly encouraged to e-mail titles, abstracts, and other relevant bibliographic information (e.g., journal name and volume/page numbers if already published) to Tom Phillips (<a href="mailto: phillips@tworks.llnl.gov">phillips@tworks.llnl.gov</a>).  Authors are urged to provide such information at the <I>submission</I> stage, rather than waiting until a publication has appeared in print, so that other scientists may be informed of their work at the earliest possible date.
<p>
