<H1>AMIP Modeling Groups</H1>
<P></P>
<HR>
<P>A list of the AMIP modeling groups and their locations. Hyperlinks connect
to further information on each model's features, and selected properties are
compared across the models in a <A HREF="modldoc/amip/10sumtbls.html">series of
tables</A>. <A HREF="../mccravy/amipemail.html">Addresses</A> of AMIP
representatives also are provided.
</P>
