<a name = "AboutCS">
<IMG SRC ="Images/RedFade.GIF"><br>
<IMG SRC ="Images/AboutCommService.GIF"><P>

<STRONG>The Community Service Division</STRONG> arranges cultural
activities in music, dance, theater, special attractions, and the visual
arts, including off-campus sites throughout the island of O`ahu and 
all neighbor islands. 
<P>
In 1995-96, the Division is coordinating tours by twenty ensembles 
from outside the state, including the Ballet Jazz du Montreal, Tandy 
Beal & Company, the Ballet Folclorico do Brazil, and the Peking 
Acrobats. The Division also tours Hawai`i-based artists 
widely throughout the state.
</a>
<P>
