<center>
<img src ="IMAGES/OSAAddress.GIF"><br>
</center>

<P>

Academic advising is available Monday through Friday during office hours and on Saturday by appointment from 8:00 am - 12 noon.  To make an appointment, or if you have any questions regarding registration or academic issues, please call 956-8400.
<P>
<A NAME = "CREDITREGINFO">
<HR>

