<BODY bgcolor = #FFFFFF>


<center>
<P>

<img src = "images/PSP2.GIF">
<br>
<img src = "images/AboutOurProgramTitle.GIF">

<P>
</center>
<A HREF="AboutOurPrograms.HTML">[About Our Programs] </A>
<A HREF="ClassSchedule.HTML">[Class Schedule] </A>
<A HREF="Instructors.HTML">[Instructors] </A>
<A HREF="MailingList.HTML">[Mailing List] </A>
<A HREF="Maps.HTML">[Maps]</A><A HREF="http://www-ccecs.arthum.hawaii.edu/OSA/Home.HTML#NONCREDITREGINFO">[Registration Info] </A>
<A HREF="Search.HTML">[Search] </A>
<A HREF="WhoToCall.HTML">[Who to Call] </A>

<P>

<ul>
<li> <strong>CONTINUING EDUCATION FOR PROFESSIONAL PROGRAM</strong><br>
	Programs provided for professionals to stay abreast of changes<br> 
	in their fields of employment</li>
<P>
<li> <strong>PERSONAL AND CAREER DEVELOPMENT PROGRAMS</strong><br>
	Programs provided for those seeking to acquire new life skills,<br> 
	to improve career opportunities, expand communication and language skills,<br> 
	or to enhance interpersonal relations</li>
<P>
<li> <strong>PERSONAL ENRICHMENT AND COMMUNITY INTEREST PROGRAMS</strong><br>
	Programs provided for personal enrichment and recreation as well as 
	programs intended to bring the resources of the University to bear on community issues and needs</li>
<P>
<li> <strong>SMALL BUSINESS MANAGEMENT PROGRAM</strong><br>
	Programs intended to provide small business owners and entreprenuers practical knowledge and 
	an understanding of the innovations relating to business practices</li>
<P>
</ul>
<P>
<P>
<img align = left border = 0 src = "images/PSPMontage.GIF">
<font size = 2>
<strong>LEARN</strong> a new skill, pursue a special interest, and meet new friends! 
Professional and Special Programs (PSP) offers you access to lifelong
learning opportunities and has over 40 years of experience providing interesting
and affordable educational programs to adults.<P>

In our noncredit program we offer you the
chance to upgrade professional skills, discover new talents, improve your
physical and emotional well-being, and explore the rich cultural traditions of
both East and West.  Our classes are held on the Manoa Campus and at various
off-campus locations, at times and places that are convenient for you.
<pre>



</pre>
<font size = 3>
