<HTML>

<HEAD> <TITLE> Small Business Management Program </TITLE> </HEAD>

<BODY bgcolor ="#ffffff"> <center> 
<img src ="Images/PSPAddress2.GIF"> <hr> 
<img src ="Images/SBMP2.GIF"></center> <hr> <P> 
<P>

<A HREF= "http://www-ccecs.arthum.hawaii.edu/PSP/AboutOurPrograms.HTML">[About Our Programs] </A>
<A HREF= "http://www-ccecs.arthum.hawaii.edu/PSP/ClassSchedule.HTML">[Class Schedule] </A>
<A HREF= "http://www-ccecs.arthum.hawaii.edu/PSP/Instructors.HTML">[Instructors] </A>
<A HREF= "http://www-ccecs.arthum.hawaii.edu/PSP/MailingList.HTML">[Mailing List] </A>
<A HREF= "http://www-ccecs.arthum.hawaii.edu/PSP/Maps.HTML">[Maps]</A>
<A HREF="http://www-ccecs.arthum.hawaii.edu/OSA/Home.HTML#NONCREDITREGINFO">[Registration Info] </A><br>
<A HREF= "http://www-ccecs.arthum.hawaii.edu/PSP/Search.HTML">[Search] </A>
<A HREF= "http://www-ccecs.arthum.hawaii.edu/PSP/WhoToCall.HTML">[Who to Call] </A>
<P>
The <strong>Small Business Management Program</strong> offers noncredit, evening and weekend courses
designed to provide continuing business education directed towards the
development of managerial and entrepreneurial skills.  Programs are intended
to provide small business owners and entrepreneurs practical knowledge and an
understanding of basic principles and innovations relating to business practices. Instructors,
either practitioners in the field or University of Hawai`i faculty, have had
wide practical business experience.  <strong> Enrollment is
limited.</strong><P>

Tuition is tax-deductible under certain circumstances and certificates are
awarded in recognition of an attendance record of at least eighty percent of
the class sessions. <P>

<P>
<P> </BODY>

