<TITLE>Welcome!</TITLE>
<BODY bgcolor="#ffffff">

<pre>

Thank you for your interest in the University of
Hawai`i at Manoa College of Continuing Education
and Community Service.  Our goal is to support the
people of Hawai`i by providing opportunities for the
educational growth and developement of its adult
community members.  Whether you are simply interested
in knowing more about the College or are actively
pursing you own continuing education, we are here
to serve you.

Please don not hesitate to contact our offices if you
have any questions or concerns about the programs
offered by the College of if we can be of assistance.


                                Sincerely,
                                Robert E. Gibson
                                Interim Dean
