HPER 581-U, Innovative Ideas for Elementary PE (1 credit)</strong>
This course is designed to help elementary teachers develop and learn
new skills and techniques to motivate their students in physical
education activities.<br>
Instructor:	Wilfred Okabe<p>

*	Sec 41 (Kona), WThF, 8 am-12 noon, June 12-14, Keauhou Beach
Hotel, $75 (residents)/$130 (non-residents) plus $3 materials fee.<P><strong>

