Develop and learn new skills and techniques to motivate students in
physical education activities. Especially for elementary and physical
education teachers.<br>
Instructor:	Wilfred Okabe<p>

*	Sec 1 (Hilo), MTWThFS, 8 am- 1 pm, June 17-22, Location TBA, $150
