Institute Fee for both EdCI 583P SEC. 1101 CRN 1125 & SEC. 1201 CRN
4395:  [$475 for participants who have not previously enrolled in a
DASH institute.] [$325 for participants who want to repeat an
institute grade level taken previously.  Certification as DASH teacher
required.  Bring your own Teacher Set.]  Payable to RCUH upon receipt
of confirmation letter.<p><strong>

PICD:NATURAL SC -- DASH FOR GRADES K-3 OR GRADES 4-5 [Summer (3 crs)
and Fall (3 crs), 15-day institute - to receive full certification in
the DASH program completion of both EdCI 583P SEC. 1111 CRN 1126 AND
EdCI 583P SEC. 1211 CRN 4396 is required.]<br>
EdCI 583P SEC. 1111 CRN 1126<br></strong>
June 1-3, 5, 6, 8-12, 1996<br>
M-W, F, S, M-F 8:30 am-4:00 pm<br>
Maui - Wailuku Elementary School<br>
