<H2>HAWAI'I PUBLIC EMPLOYMENT RELATIONS ACT</center>
<center>HRS, Chapter 89</center>
<center>Collective Bargaining in Public Employment</H2>
<img src = "Images/thumb.gif"><P>
</center>


Phone: (808) 956-7145; FAX: (808) 956-2023;<br>
E-Mail: <A HREF = "MAILTO: puette@hawaii.edu">puette@hawaii.edu</A>;<br>
To return to CLEAR's <A HREF = "CLEARHome.HTML">Home Page</A>

<img src = "Images/Swash4.GIF"><p>
<strong>NOTE:</strong><br>
Unlike other sections of this Web site which summarize and describe the main features of State and Federal Labor Laws, what follows here is not a summary, but the actual text of the collective bargaining law for Hawai'i's State & County employees, as last amended by the 1996 session of the State Legislature.
<HR SIZE = 4><P>

<H3>SECTIONS:</H3>

